[03:24] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'this over here as well on the left side. Add in a transform. Go to frame 30. Create a key frame on center X and angle. And then let\'s go to frame 60 and'

[03:36] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'sort of move it to the left. And then change the angle as well. Right. So maybe we want to change the center X even more over here. And just'

[03:50] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
