AUDIO: 'drop shadow. Select this tool. Click on add. And [music] this will add in a drop shadow like this. You can definitely change the blur [music] amount distance and increase the strength. Let\'s um take'

[04:15] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'this wood texture and merge it with this drop shadow. And this will bring the wood texture in the front. We\'ll hit CtrlT on the keyboard. But we have this resolution changed. So the wood node'

[04:29] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'over here. We will add in a letter box to this. So that this is going to be in 1920x 1080 resolution. And now you can like change the texture or the color of the wood. So you can add in a color'

[04:42] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'corrector after this and change the brightness and all that stuff over here. We change the saturation, gain and all that stuff. And if you notice any line in the node over here, as you can see, you can go to either of these polygon'

[04:55] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
